4 NEW SECTION. Section 4. Sales of alternative nicotine products or vapor products through
5 vending machines restricted. (1) Alternative nicotine products and vapor products may be sold through a
6 vending machine only in places where alcoholic beverages are sold and consumed on the premises and where
7 the vending machine is under the direct line-of-sight supervision of the owner or an employee of the
8 establishment. The alternative nicotine products or vapor products must be in a vending machine that contains
9 only alternative nicotine products or vapor products.
10 (2) Alternative nicotine products or vapor products may not be sold through a vending machine
11 that is located in a restaurant unless the restaurant has a bar, the restaurant area shares seating with the bar
12 area, and the vending machine meets the requirements of subsection (1).
13 (3) The sale of alternative nicotine products or vapor products from a vending machine under the
14 direct line-of-sight supervision of an owner or employee is considered a sale of alternative nicotine products or
15 vapor products by the owner or employee for the purposes of [section 3].
16
17 NEW SECTION. Section 5. Civil penalties -- license suspension. (1) Failure to obtain a license as
18 required by [section 2] or failure to post signs as provided in [section 3] is punishable by a civil penalty of $100.
19 The department may collect the penalty in the manner provided for the collection of other debts.
20 (2) A person who violates [section 3(1)] or [section 4] at any one location within a 3-year period
21 shall be punished as follows:
22 (a) A first through third offense is punishable by a verbal notification of violation.
23 (b) A fourth offense is punishable by a written notice of violation to be sent by the department of
24 public health and human services to the owner of the establishment.
25 (c) A fifth offense is punishable by assessment of a $500 fine against the owner of the
26 establishment.
27 (d) A sixth offense is punishable by suspension of the license for 3 months.
